{"tid":1422000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經過今日 民間記招其實可以有全面方向","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T19:02:59.000Z","uid":235465,"like":103,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"56139d733c6187997b2a86c802f40b8ef3fd6225","tid":1422000,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:30:35.000Z","msg":"其實可以分幾種<br />\n(1)事件後記招<br />\n好似今日咁 班狗屈示威者點點點 講曬大話<br />\n咁我地D記招就可以打反擊 踢爆佢地講大話 同埋有幾錯<br />\n例如之前TATP 汽油彈咁 如果開公開記招踢爆 可以降低部分人對警隊信任程度<br />\n<br />\n(2)平和期-打感情牌<br />\n琴日黃大仙妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我最記得班狗最後講過兩個字 &quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">煽動</span>&quot;<br />\n事實上我地更應該做 就係平和期期間攻破li類論點<br />\n例如搵D年輕人上黎講下 自己為咩要出黎 無比人煽動<br />\n事實上大部分年輕人擔心自己未來 想要翻自己個未來 先會出黎<br />\n其他時間 可以搵D街坊出黎講下 自己踢拖出街點比班狗搞<br />\n例如琴晚凌晨將軍澳<br />\n<br />\n簡單D 類似電台節目咁做個訪問記招<br />\n<br />\n(3)理性類<br />\n搵專家分析 例如之前個極搞笑1kg TATP<br />\n可以搵D學者出黎講下幾離譜(如果有 睇連登仔人脈有幾廣了)<br />\n<br />\n(4)宣傳類<br />\n宣傳未來活動 connect連登同連登外既人<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提<br />\n8月6日警招應對影音組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JABufhcUYmZyWlGGxMdp9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJABufhcUYmZyWlGGxMdp9A&d=Lhg6HStjEOrAYLon%2F%2F44J3aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=8d4668c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JABufhcUYmZyWlGGxMdp9A</a><br />\n<br />\n入嚟幫手準備片聽日播！！<br />\n多謝警察教我地點開記招！！"},{"pid":"680ad07f9d7a981401737fde61ea875e9925fd3f","tid":1422000,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7780cc34094a64f3b86c62ef8a909859f46263da","tid":1422000,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"